data.description: Rarely available in Watercrest Community of Parkland "Bellingham Model". Amazing views of the 150 acre lake, The home has over 4200+ sqft 5 bedroom-5 bathroom, 3 car garage, office/den, large loft upstairs masterpiece. Brand new kitchen cabinets installed. The chef's kitchen is a culinary dream which features gas stove, double ovens, overiszed kitchen island, 2 pantries and SS appliances. Recessed lighting illuminating your path. All impact windows and doors. Volume ceilings create an inviting atmosphere. Step outside to the covered lanai offering breathtaking waterfront views as far as your eyes can see. Watercrest's community has a resort-style clubhouse, resort style pool, kids playground,gym,  and gated community provide endless entertainment options and security.
